## Risk Assessment

| Risk | Severity | Likelihood | Mitigation |
|------|----------|------------|------------|
| Tests are flaky (intermittent failures) | High | Medium | Use explicit waits, mock time, avoid network calls |
| Tests take too long (>10 min) | Medium | Medium | Parallelize, optimize setup/teardown, focus on critical paths |
| False positives (tests pass but bugs exist) | High | Low | Use semantic assertions, test real user flows, review coverage |
| IndexedDB quota issues in CI | Medium | Low | Use smaller datasets in CI, test quota errors separately |
| Service Worker interference | Medium | Medium | Clear Service Worker state in `beforeEach`, use test-specific scope |

